OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFeeling rather warm in southern
OL,6,Fparts of the region with lengthy sunny
OL,7,Fperiods. Somewhat cloudier, breezier
OL,8,Fand feeling cooler further north with
OL,9,Fa small chance of a light shower,
OL,10,Fespecially across the Peak District.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry night will then follow
OL,13,Fwith light winds for all by the early
OL,14,Fhours. A mix of cloud and clearer
OL,15,Fspells, a rather mild night for most.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FSunday will be a fine day with
OL,18,Flight winds and a mix of fair weather
OL,19,Fcloud and sunny spells. Feeling a
OL,20,Flittle warmer for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
