OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Cloudier
OL,7,Ffrom Tuesday with a little rain at
OL,8,Ftimes towards the north. Turning
OL,9,Fwindier, especially by Wednesday.
OL,10,FRemaining rather warm throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
